### Patient Management Endpoints Testing

### Create a new patient
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/patients
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "mrn": "MRN-001",
  "firstName": "Juan",
  "lastName": "Pérez",
  "age": 45,
  "gender": "M",
  "status": "ADMITTED",
  "diagnosis": "Hipertensión",
  "roomNumber": "101",
  "bedNumber": "A",
  "notes": "Patient with chronic hypertension"
}

### Get all patients
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/patients

### Get patient by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/patients/1

### Get patient by MRN
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/patients/mrn/MRN-001

### Get patients by status
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/patients/status/ADMITTED

### Get critical patients
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/patients/critical

### Update patient
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/patients/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "mrn": "MRN-001",
  "firstName": "Juan",
  "lastName": "Pérez",
  "age": 46,
  "gender": "M",
  "status": "STABLE",
  "diagnosis": "Hypertension - Controlled",
  "roomNumber": "102",
  "bedNumber": "B",
  "notes": "Patient showing improvement"
}

### Delete patient
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/patients/1

### Create critical patient
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/patients
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "mrn": "MRN-CRITICAL-001",
  "firstName": "María",
  "lastName": "García",
  "age": 72,
  "gender": "F",
  "status": "CRITICAL",
  "diagnosis": "Acute Myocardial Infarction",
  "roomNumber": "ICU-02",
  "bedNumber": "3",
  "notes": "Requires continuous monitoring"
}

### Create stable patient
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/patients
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "mrn": "MRN-STABLE-001",
  "firstName": "Carlos",
  "lastName": "López",
  "age": 35,
  "gender": "M",
  "status": "STABLE",
  "diagnosis": "Post-operative care",
  "roomNumber": "201",
  "bedNumber": "C",
  "notes": "Post-surgical recovery proceeding normally"
}

### Actuator - Health check
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/actuator/health

### Actuator - Application info
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/actuator/info

### Actuator - Metrics
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/actuator/metrics

### OpenAPI Documentation
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/swagger-ui.html

### OpenAPI JSON Schema
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/openapi.json
